T12TD4304E:379a-40: // /'di ni chos ldan ra za ba dang /
T12TD4304E:379a-41: yar klungs ba grags pa rgyal mtshan gyis bsgyur ba'o //
T12TD4304E:379a-42: slad kyi sa gsum na 'gran zla dang bral ba'i thams cad mkhyen pa chen po don gyi slad du mtshan nas smos te /
T12TD4304E:379a-43: byang chub rtse mo'i zhal snga nas bsgyur ba la /
T12TD4304E:379a-44: slar yang de nyid kyi bkas rjes su gnang ba la brten te /
T12TD4304E:379a-46: skyes bu dam pa rnams kyi bka' drin gyis legs par bskyangs pa'i dge slong nam mkha' bzang pos /
T12TD4304E:379a-47: sh'akya'i dge slong sdom brtson dam pa rnams kyi gtsug rgyan /
T12TD4304E:379a-48: sde snod gsum gyi glegs bam gcig pu /
T12TD4304E:379a-49: skad gnyis smra ba'i dbang po dpal ldan blo gros brtan pa'i phyag bris kyi rgya dpe la gtugs nas /
T12TD4304E:379a-50: dpal ae'i chos grva chen por bsgyur cing zhus te dag par bgyis so /
